0problems%20are.%20I%20want%20to%20understand%20what%20my%20responsibilities%20are...%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20voters%20at%20her%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20also%20referred%20to%20her%20brother%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20defended%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20in%20the%20April-June%20general%20election%20(he%20secured%20nearly%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes)%20but%20resigned%20in%20June%20after%20also%20winning%20the%20family%20stronghold%20of%20Raebareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20seat%20earlier%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-priyanka-gandhi-be-a-better-mp-for-wayanad-rahul-gandhi-responds-6861236%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWill%20Priyanka%20Be%20A%20Better%20MP%20For%20Wayanad%3F%20Rahul%20Responds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20(many%20of)%20you%20came%20to%20hear%20me%20because%20of%20your%20love%20for%20my%20brother.%20I%20am%20his%20sister%20and%20I%20know%20what%20a%20heavy%20heart%20he%20had%20when%20he%20left%20you.%20You%20gave%20him%20love%20when%20everyone%20turned%20their%20back%20on%20him.%20It%20is%20you...%20each%20one%20of%20you...%20who%20gave%20him%20courage.%20You%20are%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-election-affidavit-robert-vadra-bjp-targets-priyanka-gandhi-on-poll-affidavit-husband-robert-vadra-replies-6864533%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Targets%20Priyanka%20On%20Poll%20Affidavit%2C%20Robert%20Vadra%20Replies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayanad%20votes%20on%20November%2013.%20Nearly%2050%20other%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20by-polls%20will%20be%20held%20next%20month%2C%20with%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20election%20on%20Nov%2013%20and%20the%20second%20on%20Nov%2020.%3C