%20of%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20desperation%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20war%2C%20some%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20he%20was%20expecting%20to%20see%20North%20Korean%20troops%20in%20battle%20within%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20another%20nation%20had%20committed%20ground%20troops%20to%20the%20main%20war%20effort%20in%20Ukraine.%20Both%20sides%20have%20long%20received%20weapons%20and%20advice%20from%20their%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Thursday%2C%20Zelenskyy%20said%20he%20had%20information%20indicating%20that%20North%20Korea%20was%20preparing%20to%20send%2010%2C000%20troops%20to%20occupied%20areas%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20alarmed%20officials%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20which%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-ukraine-weapons-big-difference-russia-north-korea-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econdemned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20deployment.%20It%20threatened%20to%20send%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine%20as%20part%20of%20a%20series%20of%20phased%20countermeasures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERutte%20said%20that%20NATO%20urged%20both%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20to%20pull%20back%20immediately%2C%20citing%20risks%20to%20both%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20Euro-Atlantic%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20undermines%20peace%20on%20the%20Korean%20peninsula%20and%20fuels%20the%20Russian%20war%20against%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Putin%20last%20Friday%20seemed%20unmoved%20by%20external%20criticism%2C%20saying%20whether%20Russia%20deploys%20North%20Korean%20troops%20is%20Russia's%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-says-it-is-our-affair-if-russia-uses-north-korean-