%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718cb1901ea6d83dee3586b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaquis%20started%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Maui%20to%20be%20with%20her%20husband.%20%3Cp%3ESophie%20Daquis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220132782e-fee4-4964-8d00-fd925e758b2c%5C%22%3EChange%20started%20with%20small%20habits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20thinking%20to%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20does%20this%20stop%3F%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3B%20How%20can%20I%20fix%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20because%20I%20was%20just%20always%20exhausted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaui%20slowed%20me%20down.%20There's%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20on%20the%20island.%20People's%20mindsets%20and%20values%20there%20are%20so%20different%20from%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20really%20reevaluate%20everything%20I'd%20been%20told%20about%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20into%20slower%20living%20started%20with%20small%20habits%20like%20taking%20a%20walk%20on%20my%20lunch%20break%2C%20looking%20at%20my%20phone%20less%2C%20enjoying%20my%20cup%20of%20coffee%20without%20any%20distractions%2C%20and%20journaling%20in%20the%20morning.%20At%20first%2C%20that%20was%20what%20slow%20living%20was%20for%20me%E2%80%94rearranging%20my%20days%20and%20my%20life%20to%20physically%20slow%20down.%20Just%20those%20little%20changes%20made%20a%20world%20of%20a%20difference%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20else%20can%20I%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20embark%20on%20something%20different%20career-wise.%20I%20had%20been%20planning%20to%20transition%20from%20full-time%20to%20part-time%20work%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%20so%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20save%20up%20in%20advance%20to%20give%20myself%20some%20cushion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20also%20just%20bought%20a%20house%20and%20were%20able%20to%20supplement%20our%20income%20by%20renting%20out%20a%20portion%20of%20it%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boss%20allowed%20me%20to%20work%20remotely%20and%20switch%20to%20part%20time%20and%20I%20started%20experimenting%20with%20YouTube.%20Initially%2C%20I%20was%20just%20trying%20out%20different%20formats%2C%20like%20footage%20of%20Hawaii%20or%20home-renovation%20videos.%20When%20I%20started%20documenting%20my%20slow-living%20journey%2C%20it%20resonated%20and%20that's%20what%20my%20channel%20became.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20video%20that%20really%20gained%20traction%20with%20my%20audience%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fapp%3Ddesktop%26v%3DVTniB-wsgI0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMy%20Calm%20Evening%20Routine%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20where%20I%20shared%20how%20I%20unwind%20after%20a%20typical%20day%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20goal%20became%20to%20create%20a%20library%20of%20content%20on%20slow-living%20and%20minimalism.%20I%20started%20doing%20YouTube%20more%20and%20my%209-to-5%20less%20until%20I%20was%20able%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20YouTuber.%20I%20am%20so%20blessed%20to%20have%20YouTube%20because%20it%20really%20allows%20me%20to%20work%20when%20I%20want%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20to%20Lisbon%2C%20Portugal.%20We%20lived%20in%20Portugal%20for%20eight%20months%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20weren't%20able%20to%20stop%20thinking%20about%20it.%20Even%20though%20we%20are%20now%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20always%20live%20a%20slow%20living%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sophie%20Daquis%20sits%20on%20grass%20holding%20a%20small%20dog.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718cbf201ea6d83dee358a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaquis%20makes%20videos%20that%20showcase%20her%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%20%3Cp%3ESophie%20Daquis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed409b9f-e7d4-497b-a74a-6b3ad80fa251%5C%22%3EI%20prioritized%20finding%20time%20for%20the%20things%20I%20enjoy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20more%20flexibility%20in%20my%20work%20life%2C%20I%20became%20really%20intentional%20about%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20prioritize%20and%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20my%20time.%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20journaling%20and%20reflected%20on%20what's%20important%20in%20my%20life%20and%20how%20I%20can%20prioritize%20those%20things.%20I%20stopped%20forcing%20myself%20to%20attend%20every%20work%20function.%20I%20avoided%20overloading%20my%20weekends%20and%20focused%20on%20just%20one%20or%20two%20important%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20slow%20living%20has%20transitioned%20into%20a%20whole%20mindset%20for%20me.%20It's%20like%20a%20lens%20through%20which%20I%20look%20at%20the%20world%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20moved%20away%20from%20the%20need%20to%20hustle.%20I%20honor%20how%20I%20feel%20more%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20rush.%20I%20believe%20that%20things%20will%20happen%20on%20their%20own%20timeline.%20I%20do%20work%20hard%20when%20I%20need%20to%2C%20but%20I%20also%20prioritize%20balance%2C%20so%20I'll%20then%20give%20myself%20time%20to%20regenerate%20and%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20enjoyed%20the%20simple%20moments%20in%20life%2C%20but%20slowing%20down%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20enjoy%20them%20more%20fully%20and%20without%20the%20nagging%20feeling%20that%20I%20should%20be%20doing%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-9-5-for-slow-minimalist-life-as-youtuber-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730113858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-9-5-f