%20General%20Catalyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReflexivity%20was%20founded%20by%20two%20former%20hedge%20fund%20traders%20who%20were%20all%20too%20familiar%20with%20the%20woes%20of%20wrangling%20disparate%20data%20sets%20to%20find%20an%20investing%20edge%2C%20or%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20to%20not%20miss%20out%20on%20an%20opportunity%20others%20are%20seizing.%20The%20startup%20aims%20to%20mitigate%20that%20by%20combining%20third-party%20data%20from%20a%20dozen%20providers%20like%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20and%20newsfeeds%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20proprietary%20internal%20information%2C%20for%20a%20full-view%20analysis%20and%20also%20flagging%20the%20potential%20impact%20world%20and%20market%20events%20may%20have%20on%20a%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20an%20investor%20inside%20a%20major%20hedge%20fund%2C%20one%20big%20fear%20that%20is%20always%20present%20is%20that%20you%20are%20going%20to%20miss%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Jan%20Szilagyi%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20exciting%20to%20have%20a%20trade%20that%20you%20are%20the%20only%20one%20that's%20in%20it%2C%20but%20the%20thing%20that%20is%20far%20worse%20is%20to%20miss%20on%20the%20trade%20that%20everybody%20else%20but%20you%20is%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-year-old%20startup%20recently%20changed%20its%20name%20to%20more%20closely%20align%20with%20how%20the%20platform%20helps%20with%20the%20investment%20process%2C%20Szilagyi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReflexivity%20is%20the%20act%20of%20examining%20one's%20own%20assumptions%2C%20beliefs%2C%20and%20judgment%20systems%2C%20and%20thinking%20carefully%20and%20critically%20about%20how%20these%20influence%20the%20research%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20term%20popularized%20by%20legendary%20investor%20George%20Soros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESzilagyi%20was%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%20at%20firms%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstanley-druckenmiller-q1-portfolio-why-sell-nvidia-stock-ai-hype-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDruckenmiller's%20%3C%2Fa%3EDuquesne%20Capital%20Management%20and%20Fortress%20Investment%20Group.%20The%20fintech's%20president%20and%20other%20cofounder%2C%20Giuseppe%20Sette%2C%20also%20worked%20in%20asset%20management%20including%20a%20stint%20at%20macro%20giant%20Brevan%20Howard.%20They%20remember%20the%20investment%20analysis%20process%20as%20one%20that%20%26quot%3Bseemed%20hopelessly%20broken%26quot%3B%20because%20critical%20data%20sources%20were%20fragmented%20and%20spread%20out%20across%20different%20providers%20and%20systems%2C%20Szilagyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20estimates%20the%20potential%20market%20for%20its%20services%20is%20%2416.4%20billion.%20Reflexivity%20so%20far%20has%20about%2020%20institutional%20clients%2C%20tallying%20some%2015%2C000%20individual%20users.%20Clients%20include%20trading%20platforms%20like%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20banks%2C%20including%20Japan's%20largest%20in%20MUFG%2C%20and%20several%20hedge%20funds%2C%20including%20Millennium%20Management%2C%20Soros%20Fund%2C%20and%20ExodusPoint.%20The%20startup%20was%20highlighted%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-best-fintech-startups-according-to-vc-2023%23toggle-ai-47%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20up-and-coming%20fintechs%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20valuation%20between%20%24115%20million%20and%20%24150%20million%2C%20Szilagyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bb6e2b7-a338-4061-9625-c98518e78eff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Reflexivity%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upstart's%20platform%20lets%20stock-picking%20investors%20analyze%20data%20that%20covers%20about%2040%2C000%20securities%20from%20a%20dozen%20different%20providers%2C%20including%20Refinitiv%20and%20the%20London%20Stock%20Exchange%20Group%2C%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global.%20It%20is%20also%20built%20to%20alert%20customers%2C%20mostly%20discretionary%20investors%20who%20work%20at%20hedge%20funds%20and%20asset%20managers%2C%20to%20market%20events%20and%20their%20potential%20ripple%20effects%20on%20a%20given%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20a%20big%20move%20in%20treasury%20yields%2C%20Reflexivity%20will%20automatically%20examine%20the%20ripple%20effects%20and%20see%20how%20that%20could%20impact%20banking%20stocks.%20In%20this%20hypothetical%20example%2C%20Reflexivity%20would%20see%20that%20its%20user%2C%20say%20a%20hedge%20fund%20trader%2C%20has%20Wells%20Fargo%20stock%20in%20her%20portfolio%2C%20and%20flag%20to%20her%20that%20Wells%20Fargo%20stock%20historically%20reacts%20very%20well%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%2C%20a%20proprietary%20knowledge%20graph%20and%20generative%20AI-powered%20user%20interface%20helps%20users%20connect%20the%20dots%20and%20better%20understand%20investing%20relationships%2C%20Szilagyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESzilyagyi%20says%20he%20also%20has%20an%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20many%20Wall%20Street%20technologists%20are%20facing%20with%20hallucinations%2C%20or%20generative%20AI's%20tendency%20to%20make%20up%20answers%20that%20are%20presented%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReflexivity's%20answer%20is%20a%20so-called%20closed%20system%2C%20wherein%20the%20AI%20models%20can%20only%20pull%20answers%20from%20data%20that's%20been%20pre-vetted%20by%20the%20startup.%20The%20reason%20other%20models%2C%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20hallucinate%20is%20because%20it%20operates%20on%20an%20open%20system%20that%20takes%20in%20data%20from%20anywhere%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20Szilagyi%20said.%20If%20it%20can't%20find%20anything%2C%20it'll%20be%20inclined%20to%20make%20up%20an%20answer%20because%20these%20tools%20are%20built%20to%20deliver%20some%20kind%20of%20answer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20Reflexivity%20also%20programmed%20its%20models%20to%20not%20force%20an%20answer%20to%20every%20question.%20About%205%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20Reflexivity%20will%20say%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20answer%20a%20given%20question%20if%20it's%20unable%20to%20generate%20an%20answer%20from%20the%20data%20it's%20been%20given%2C%20Szilagyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20finance%20professionals%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20get%20the%20candid%20and%20honest%20answer%20is%20absolutely%20critical%20because%20it%20only%20takes%20one%2C%20two%20hallucinations%20to%20be%20extremely%20costly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20trading%2C%26quot%3B%20Szilagyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a8f4bab-cdf0-4617-9ace-8234588d378c%5C%22%3EHere's%20Reflexivity's%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20Series%20B.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E(Because%20the%20startup%20only%20recently%20changed%20its%20name%2C%20these%20slides%20include%20its%20former%20name%2C%20Toggle%20AI.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221590%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pitch%20deck%20Reflexivity%2C%20formerly%20Toggle%20AI%2C%20used%20for%20its%20Series%20B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671aa6d8a0a0cc14f223c07b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPitch%20deck%20that%20Reflexivity%2C%20formerly%20Toggle%20AI%2C%20used%20for%20its%20%2430%20million%20Series%20B%3Cp%3EReflexivity%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pitch%20deck%20Reflexivity%2C%20formerly%20Toggle%20AI%2C%20used%20for%20its%20Series%20B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671aa6d8a0a0cc14f223c079%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPitch%20deck%20that%20Reflexivity%2C%20formerly%20Toggle%20AI%2C%20used%20for%20its%20%2430%20million%20Series%20B%3Cp