oling%3C%2Fa%3E%20outright%2C%20yet%20our%20desire%20is%20to%20support%20our%20children%2C%20who%20are%20ages%204%2C%206%2C%208%2C%2010%2C%20and%2013%2C%20set%20themselves%20up%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20most%20families%20think%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-529-plan-to-pay-for-middle-school-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20savings%2C%20they%20picture%20a%20529%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20we%20chose%20custodial%20accounts%20under%20the%20Uniform%20Transfer%20to%20Minors%20Act%2C%20or%20UTMAs%2C%20for%20our%20kids.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-parents-should-know-about-529s-and-how-use-them-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20529%20savings%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20you%20to%20save%20money%20for%20a%20beneficiary%2C%20your%20child%2C%20and%20use%20it%20to%20pay%20for%20education%20expenses.%20You%20can%20pay%20for%20tuition%2C%20but%20also%20boarding%2C%20and%20books.%20Some%20parents%20use%20it%20to%20pay%20for%20private%20school%20before%20their%20kids%20are%20off%20to%20college.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fmerrill-edge-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20UTMA%20custodial%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20managed%20by%20the%20parents%20until%20the%20child%20is%20either%2018%20or%2021%2C%20at%20which%20point%20they%20gain%20full%20control%20of%20the%20money.%20They%20can%20use%20it%20to%20pay%20for%20college%20or%20make%20big%20investments%20such%20as%20buying%20a%20car.%20The%20accounts%20can%20contain%20money%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20fine%20art%2C%20and%20even%20patents.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20we%20decided%20UTMA%20accounts%20were%20best%20for%20our%20family%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a27220d-540c-43cd-a7c1-0e9d0d71dc4e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20a%20UTMA%20custodial%20account%2C%20money%20belongs%20to%20the%20child%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20for%20parents%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20funds%20in%20a%20UTMA%20account%20are%20legally%20considered%20the%20child's%20property%2C%20Andy%20Esser%2C%20a%20financial%20advisor%20at%20investing%20firm%20Edward%20Jones%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20this%20status%20%26quot%3Bcould%20provide%20some%20protection%20from%20the%20parent's%20creditors%2C%26quot%3B%20Esser%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20This%20doesn't%20rule%20out%20529%20plans%2C%20which%20can%20be%20set%20up%20with%20either%20a%20parent%20or%20a%20child%20as%20the%20legal%20owner%3B%20additionally%2C%20some%20states%20do%20offer%20creditor%20protection%20for%20529%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20might%20hope%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimportant-things-to-know-as-the-executor-of-an-estate-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskip%20estate%20probate%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20UTMA%20account%2C%20Esser%20notes%20that's%20also%20not%20completely%20true.%20If%20the%20custodian%20dies%2C%20a%20new%20one%20must%20be%20appointed%2C%20and%20if%20the%20minor%20dies%2C%20the%20account%20typically%20becomes%20part%20of%20the%20minor's%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213280c36-0e41-4fa1-8e06-8c3fdf5b7a92%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUTMA%20accounts%20are%20flexible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20529%20plans%20must%20be%20used%20for%20education-related%20expenses%2C%20the%20options%20for%20UTMAs%20are%20much%20broader.%20The%20primary%20stipulation%20is%20that%20custodians%20cannot%20spend%20money%20on%20themselves%3B%20the%20money%20must%20be%20spent%20on%20something%20that%20directly%20benefits%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenefits%20may%20include%20necessary%20support%20costs%2C%20such%20as%20healthcare%2C%20or%20they%20can%20be%20big-ticket%20items.%20With%20UTMAs%2C%20our%20kids%20could%20buy%20their%20first%20cars%2C%20study%20abroad%2C%20put%20down%20payments%20on%20their%20first%20apartments%2C%20or%20even%20get%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20any%20investments%20that%20UTMA%20accounts%20make%20that%20result%20in%20income%20earned%20means%20that%20the%20income%20above%20%241%2C300%20is%20taxable%2C%20and%20the%20child%20or%20guardian%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20paying%20those.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2feb96a-910f-40dc-9f6a-ef1e36d66231%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUTMA%20accounts%20fit%20better%20with%20our%20parenting%20philosophy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20not%20aggressive%20savers%2C%20and%20having%20lived%20through%20a%20market%20crash%2C%20we%20don't%20like%20having%20too%20much%20money%20tied%20up%20in%20traditional%20investments%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20suggestions%20that%20the%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-bubble-sp500-outlook-valuations-1929-2000-hussman-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20market%20is%20bubbling%3C%2Fa%3E%20dangerously%20again%20haven't%20assuaged%20our%20concerns.%20I%20wanted%20something%20reasonably%20safe%20that%20could%20grow%20over%20time%20and%20be%20used%20in%20many%20different%20applications%2C%20with%20no%20doubt%20as%20to%20which%20person%20each%20fund%20was%20intended%20for.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe're%20not%20very%20hands-on%20with%20our%20custodial%20accounts%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20plan%20to%20keep%20huge%20amounts%20of%20money%20in%20them%2C%20ever.%20They're%20meant%20to%20supplement%20our%20children's%20needs%20at%20some%20future%20date%2C%20not%20eliminate%20their%20responsibility%20to%20study%2C%20work%2C%20and%20build%20their%20own%20savings.%20If%20someday%20we%20find%20ourselves%20doing%20better%20financially%20than%20we%20are%20now%2C%20we're%20more%20likely%20to%20help%20our%20children%20invest%20in%20something%20tangible%2C%20such%20as%20a%20vehicle%20or%20to%20help%20start%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d4657ac-9f65-486d-a93e-d6398915dd97%5C%22%3ESpecial%20needs%20can%20be%20accommodated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20children%20has%20dyslexia%20and%20dislikes%20traditional%20schooling.%20The%20flexibility%20of%20a%20UTMA%20account%20means%20that%20we%20can%20include%20all%20of%20our%20children%20equally%20without%20the%20expectation%20that%20everyone%20will%20choose%20to%20go%20to%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20UTMAs%20do%20have%20a%20bigger%20impact%20than%20529%20on%20college%20financial%20aid%20eligibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b8c6ed5-b7ae-495f-94ba-77a33bbdd563%5C%22%3EUTMA%20accounts%20are%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20our%20youngest%20was%20born%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20start%20some%20sort%20of%20savings%20for%20all%20of%20our%20kids%2C%20however%20small.%20In%20a%20tough%20quarter%2C%20they'll%20each%20be%20getting%20the%20%2425%20monthly%20minimum%2C%20and%20in%20better%20seasons%2C%20I'll%20put%20by%20whatever%20extra%20I%20can.%20If%20extended%20family%20members%20wish%20to%20contribute%20also%2C%20our%20brokerage%20accounts%20make%20it%20simple%20for%20them%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20529%20plans%2C%20UTMA%20account%20contributions%20are%20post-tax%2C%20meaning%20that%20income%20taxes%20have%20already%20been%20paid%20on%20the%20money%20being%20deposited.%20For%20moderate-income%20households%20like%20ours%2C%20however%2C%20where%20there%20is%20no%20intention%20to%20set%20aside%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20per%20account%2C%20a%20UTMA%20account%20is%20simple%20to%20open%20and%20cheap%20to%20keep%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20realize%20529%20plans%20would%20give%20us%20more%20direct%20control%20over%20our%20children's%20spending%2C%20but%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20grow%20up.%20A%20UTMA%20account%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20tools%20we%20hope%20will%20help%20them%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22