0much%20further%20they'll%20drop%20or%20where%20they%20could%20ultimately%20end%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20trending%20down%20in%202025%20as%20the%20Fed%20lowers%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20and%20inflation%20cools.%20But%20that%20forecast%20could%20change%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20economy%20evolves%20next%20year.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20Fed%20is%20poised%20to%20achieve%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20it%20successfully%20brings%20inflation%20back%20down%20to%20its%202%25%20target%20without%20sparking%20an%20economic%20downturn.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20may%20only%20decrease%20moderately%20in%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20economy%20cools%20too%20much%20and%20a%20recession%20looks%20likely%2C%20rates%20may%20fall%20more%20substantially.%20Or%2C%20if%20inflation%20stops%20decelerating%20or%20ticks%20back%20up%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20could%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-28-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730109603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-28-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20This%20week's%20labor%20market%20data%20will%20give%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20where%20mortgage%20rates%20may%20go%20in%20upcoming%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-28-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gerard%20Depardieu%20Asks%20for%20Delay%20to%20Sexual%20Assault%20Trial%20for%20Health%20Reasons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22