Besides%2C%20becoming%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftruth-promotions-companies-picking-managers-wrong-new-study-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanager%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20require%20him%20to%20go%20into%20the%20office%20every%20day%2C%20the%20way%20he%20used%20to%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20to%20see%20my%20kids%20so%20much%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BYou%20couldn't%20pay%20me%20enough%20to%20give%20that%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20his%20bosses%20it%20was%20a%20big%20change%20and%20promised%20to%20think%20it%20over.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20much%20to%20their%20surprise%2C%20he%20turned%20it%20down.%20%26quot%3BI%20talked%20about%20this%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20position%20is%20the%20correct%20fit%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20them.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20happy%20with%20what%20I'm%20doing.%20I'm%20really%20good%20at%20what%20I'm%20doing%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburnout-women-executives-hustle-culture-girlboss-work-life-balance-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClimbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20once%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20American%20dream.%20But%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I've%20been%20hearing%20about%20people%20like%20Zack%20who%20no%20longer%20aspire%20to%20the%20fancy%20titles%2C%20corner%20offices%2C%20and%20bigger%20paychecks%20that%20come%20with%20a%20promotion.%20Many%20are%20trying%20to%20fly%20under%20the%20radar%2C%20desperately%20hoping%20they%20won't%20get%20a%20tap%20on%20the%20shoulder.%20Others%20are%20outright%20declining%20promotions%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20asking%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Edemotion%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20a%20role%20with%20fewer%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Randstad%2C%20a%20global%20human-resources%20consultancy%2