quot%3B%20he%20warned%20ominously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakraborty%2C%2074%2C%20repeated%20this%20threat%2C%20calling%20the%20river%20%26quot%3Bour%20mother%26quot%3B%20and%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20say%20we%20will%20cut%20you%20up%20and%20throw%20you%2C%20not%20in%20the%20Bhagirathi%20because%20that%20is%20our%20mother%2C%20but%20we%20will%20throw%20you%20in%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakraborty%20then%20slammed%20the%20stand%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20anything...%20we%20will%20do%20anything%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20Bengal%20state%20government%20of%20not%20allowing%20the%20Hindu%20community%20to%20cast%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violent%20rhetoric%20followed%20Kabir's%20equally%20shocking%20comment%20in%20May%2C%20as%20he%20was%20campaigning%20for%20the%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20candidate%20in%20Murshidabad%20district%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20he%20reportedly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%2030%20per%20cent%20(of%20the%20people%20here)%20but%20we%20are%2070%20per%20cent...%20if%20you%20think%20you%20can%20demolish%20mosques%20and%20Muslims%20will%20sit%20back%20and%20relax...%20(you%20are%20wrong).%20I%20will%20leave%20politics%20if%20I%20don't%20drown%20you%20people%20in%20the%20Bhagirathi...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BShoot%20Me...%20Let's%20See%20How%20Many%20Bullets%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20-%20speaking%20at%20a%20membership%20drive%20-%20then%20called%20on%20BJP%20supporters%20to%20join%20the%20party's%20karyakartas.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20those%20people%20who%20will%20fight...%20who%20can%20stand%20up%20and%20say%2C%20'Shoot%20me...%20let%20me%20see%20how%20many%20bullets%20you%20have'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20over%20multiple%20incidents%20of%20pre-%20and%20post-poll%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20don't%20want%20those%20who%20join%20for%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakraborty%20then%20also%20offered%20up%20a%20second%20violent%20threat.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cut%20down%20one%20fruit%20from%20our%20trees...%20we%20will%20cut%20down%20four%20of%20yours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20Mr%20Shah%20continued%20to%20look%20on%20impassively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20One%20Takes%20Him%20Seriously...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20hit%20back%20swiftly%3B%20party%20General%20Secretary%20Jay%20Prakash%20Majumdar%20was%20quoted%20by%20a%20national%20news%20channel%20as%20dismissing%20Chakraborty%20as%20an%20inconsequential%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20takes%20him%20seriously%20as%20a%20political%20leader...%20the%20leader%20(the%20Trinamool's%20Kabir)%20whose%20comment%20he%20spoke%20about%20was%20censured%20(by%20the%20Election%20Commission).%20But%20now%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Mithun%20Chakraborty%20is%20saying%20this...%20will%20be%20also%20be%20censured%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Majumdar%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmit%20Shah%20Slams%20Mamata%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Chakraborty's%20incendiary%20speech%20Amit%20Shah%20spoke%2C%20accusing%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20her%20Trinamool%20of%20%26quot%3Bstate-sponsored%20infiltration%26quot%3B%2C%20declaring%20the%20BJP%20will%20form%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20state-sponsored%20infiltration%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20this%20is%20to%20elect%20the%20BJP%20in%202026...%20Instead%20of%20%3Cem%3ERabindrasangeet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20today%20you%20hear%20bombs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finstead-of-rabindrasangeet-bengal-hears-sound-of-bombs-amit-shah-in-kolkata-6885568%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstead%20Of%20%3Cem%3ERabindras