's%20phone%20where%20Torres%20could%20be%20heard%20frantically%20pleading%20to%20be%20released%20while%20Boone%20laughed%20and%20rebuffed%20him%20several%20times.%20In%20the%20videos%20she%20recorded%2C%20the%20victim%20could%20be%20heard%20telling%20the%20defendant%20he%20could%20not%20breathe%20and%20asking%20to%20be%20let%20out%20of%20the%20suitcase.%20Boone%20responded%20with%2C%20%E2%80%98That's%20what%20you%20get.%20%E2%80%98That's%20what%20I%20feel%20like%20when%20you%20cheat%20on%20me%2C'%20and%20other%20taunts.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20Boone%20took%20the%20stand%20in%20her%20own%20defence%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20killing%20Torres.%20She%20claimed%20her%20actions%20were%20in%20self-defence%2C%20alleging%20Torres%20previously%20abused%20her%20and%20insisting%20she%20did%20not%20mean%20to%20cause%20him%20harm.%20But%20her%20testimony%20was%20undermined%20by%20her%20earlier%20statements%20and%20video%20evidence%20that%20showed%20her%20mocking%20the%20victim%20as%20he%20pleaded%20to%20be%20freed%20from%20the%20suitcase.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20a%2010-day%20trial%2C%20the%20jury%20found%20Boone%20guilty%20of%20second-degree%20murder.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDescribing%20her%20reaction%2C%20Boone's%20attorney%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wesh.com%2Farticle%2Fsarah-boone-trial-verdict-guilty%2F62716043%5C%22%3EWESH%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20affiliate%20of%20CNN%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20shock.%20She's%20shocked%2C%20you%20know.%20She%20felt%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20she%20had%20a%20defence%2C%20as%20you%20know.%20We're%20obviously%20very%20disappointed.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20Torres's%20family%20members%2C%20the%20verdict%20provided%20some%20sense%20of%20closure%2C%20said%20state%20attorneys.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20they%20were%20finally%20just%20happy%20to%20see%20this%20case%20go%20to%20trial%20and%20be%20able%20to%20put%20this%20one%20in%20the%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20attorney.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBoone%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20her%20sentence%20on%20December%202%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20attorney's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730106960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F9efd1378_sarah-boone_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-guilty-of-killing-boyfriend-after-zipping-him-in-a-suitcase-during-hide-and-seek-game-6890288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarah%20Boone%20said%20her%20boyfriend%20got%20trapped%20in%20the%20suitcase%20during%20a%20hide-and-seek%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-guilty-of-killing-boyfriend-after-zipping-him-in-a-suitcase-during-hide-and-seek-game-6890288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Policy%20after%20policy%20made%20for%20PM%E2%80%99s%20friends%E2%80%99%3A%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20all-out%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730106413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114687119%2Cimgsize-750797.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpolicy-after-policy-made-for-pms-friends-priyanka-gandhi-vadras-all-out-attack-in-wayanad%2Farticleshow%2F114687184.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20criticized%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%2C%20alleging%20policies%20favoring%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20close%20associates.%20Addressing%20a%20gathering%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20she%20urged%20the%20protection%20of%20citizens'%20rights%20and%20received%20strong%20local%20support.%20The%20Wayanad%20bypoll%2C%20scheduled%20for%20November%2013%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0