minate-meeting-fatigue-and-be-more-productive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20future%20meetings%20better%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20called%20%26quot%3BRank%20the%20Room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20levels%20of%20involvement%20in%20a%20meeting%3A%20from%20the%20most%20important%2C%20level%20five%2C%20to%20the%20least%20important%2C%20level%20one.%20Ideally%2C%20a%20good%20meeting%20would%20be%20filled%20with%20level%20fours%20and%20fives%2C%20with%20a%20few%20threes%20for%20perspective.%20The%20others%20shouldn't%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ca544a2-94d1-4de4-8e77-dd3652c9c84f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20the%20top%2C%20at%20level%20five%2C%20is%20the%20meeting%20organizer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20the%20meeting%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%2C%20explore%20an%20issue%2C%20and%20create%20some%20results.%20They%20lead%20the%20discussion%20and%20drive%20to%20the%20outcome.%20They're%20at%20the%20top%20because%2C%20without%20them%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-ways-to-dramatically-improve-meetings-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20level%20five%20should%20evaluate%20it.%20Was%20it%20a%20good%20discussion%3F%20Did%20they%20lead%20and%20ensure%20everyone%20participated%20well%3F%20Did%20it%20last%20exactly%20as%20long%20as%20necessary%3F%20Was%20there%20a%20clear%20and%20distinct%20outcome%3F%20Does%20everyone%20know%20their%20role%20in%20the%20next%20steps%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d1b2809-49f1-492e-b230-88519feef144%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELevel-four%20people%20are%20directly%20affected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20people%20who%20are%20directly%20impacted%20by%20the%20meeting's%20outcome.%20They%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20active%20participants%20and%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20what%20