0Voyek%20first%20met%20Coolack%2C%20she%20found%20him%20charismatic%20and%20charming%2C%20saying%20he%20knew%20exactly%20what%20to%20say%20to%20make%20her%20feel%20at%20ease.%20However%2C%20their%20encounter%20took%20a%20dark%20turn%20on%20Saturday%20when%20Coolack's%20demeanour%20changed%20and%20he%20confessed%20to%20being%20wanted%20for%20murder%20in%20Texas.%20Ms%20Voyek%20shared%20her%20harrowing%20experience%2C%20warning%20others%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20trusting%20strangers%2C%20even%20if%20they%20seem%20charming%20and%20charismatic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''He%20just%20kind%20of%20got%20mad%20and%20crazy%2C%20and%20just%20bluntly%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20murdered%20his%20brother%20two%20years%20ago%2C''%20Ms%20Voyek%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20immediately%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20brother%2C%20Eddie%2C%20who%20confronted%20Coolack%20about%20the%20claim.%20Coolack%20repeated%20the%20confession%2C%20prompting%20Eddie%20to%20contact%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calhoun%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20located%20Coolack%20on%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20walking%20along%20State%20Highway%204%20outside%20Pomeroy.%20He%20was%20detained%2C%20and%20his%20identity%20was%20verified%2C%20confirming%20the%20outstanding%20murder%20warrant.%20Coolack%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Carroll%20County%20jail%2C%20awaiting%20extradition%20to%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Houston%20Police%20Department%2C%20Coolack%20is%20accused%20of%20fatally%20shooting%20his%20brother%20in%20March%202022%20and%20has%20been%20evading%20law%20enforcement%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''There%20was%20this%20sense%20of%20closure%20in%20this%20case%20once%20he%20was%20apprehended.%C2%A0I%20did%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20he%20was%20apprehended.%20I'm%20just%20happy%20to%20help%20them%20get%20the%20closure%20and%20they%20rest%20at%20ease%20that%20now%20Kyle%20is%20locked%20up%20and%20nobody%20else%20is%20in%20danger%2C''%20Sgt.%20Cullen%20Duncan%2C%20who%20is%20with%20the%20Houston%20Police%20Department%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ms%20Voyek%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20anger%20and%20unease%20following%20her%20encounter%20with%20Coolack.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20has%20learned%20a%20valuable%20lesson%20from%20this%20incident%20and%20is%20now%20urging%20others%20to%20exercise%20caution%20when%20engaging%20with%20people%20they%20don't%20know%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Just%20be%20careful%20what%20you%20do%20and%20who%20you%20talk%20to%2C%20and%20don't%20rush%20to%20let%20somebody%20in%20your%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20feels%20things%20could've%20taken%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20if%20the%20truth%20hadn't%20come%20out%20when%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Would%20he%20have%20beat%20me%3F%20Would%20he%20have%20tried%20anything%20with%20me%20and%20essentially%20killed%20me%3F%20And%20there%20are%20times%20that%20I%20wonder%20if%20it%20could%20have%20went%20there%2C''%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730105580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fcauqumd8_james-coolack_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshe-found-him-charismatic-and-charming-but-he-turned-out-to-be-a-murderer-6891194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Ms%20Voyek%20first%20met%20Coolack%2C%20she%20found%20him%20charismatic%20and%20charming%2C%20saying%20he%20knew%20exactly%20what%20to%20say%20to%20make%20her%20feel%20at%20ease.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshe-found-him-charismatic-and-charming-but-he-turned-out-to-be-a-murderer-6891194%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Kunal%20Kamra%20vs%20Ola%20CEO%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%2C%20Now%20A%20Request%20To