F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fglobal-climate-action-plans-falling-miles-short-warns-un-13243308%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Days%20Before%20Retirement%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Speaks%20On%20PM's%20Ganesh%20Puja%20Visit%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20massive%20political%20row%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20his%20home%20for%20Ganesh%20Puja%2C%20saying%20no%20judicial%20matters%20are%20discussed%20in%20such%20meetings.%C2%A0Responding%20to%20a%20question%20at%20the%20Loksatta%20annual%20lecture%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20it%20is%20a%20practice%20for%20Chief%20Ministers%20and%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20high%20courts%20to%20hold%20regular%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20think%20why%20these%20meetings.%20The%20maturity%20of%20our%20political%20system%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20deference%20to%20the%20judiciary%20even%20in%20the%20political%20class.%20It%20is%20known.%20The%20judiciary's%20budget%20is%20from%20the%20state.%20This%20budget%20is%20not%20for%20judges.%20We%20need%20new%20court%20buildings%2C%20new%20residences%20for%20judges%20in%20districts.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20Chief%20Minister's%20meetings%20are%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20he%20had%20earlier%20served%20as%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20is%20appointed%2C%20they%20go%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20house.%20Then%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20comes%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20house.%20These%20meetings%20have%20set%20agenda.%20Say%2C%2010%20projects%20are%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%2C%20what%20is%20the%20infra%2C%20the%20budget%3F%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20informs%20the%20priorities%20for%20these%20projects.%20Wouldn't%20you%20have%20to%20meet%20for%20this%3F%20If%20this%20happens%20over%20letters%2C%20the%20work%20will%20never%20get%20completed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20maturity%20in%20the%20political%20system.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20these%20meetings%2C%20never%20would%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20ask%20about%20a%20pending%20case.%20On%20August%2014%2C%20and%20January%2026%2C%20a%20wedding%20or%20mourning%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20meet%20each%20other%2C%20there%20is%20no%20bearing%20on%20judicial%20work.%20People%20ask%20what%20deals%20are%20happening.%20This%20is%20just%20part%20of%20a%20robust%20dialogue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visiting%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20residence%20and%20participating%20in%20the%20Ganesh%20Puja%20had%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%2C%20with%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Opposition%20saying%20that%20such%20meetings%20raise%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Raut%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20a%20leader%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20had%20suggested%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20should%20recuse%20himself%20from%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20tussle%20between%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20and%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20it%20is%20Ganpati%20festival.%20How%20many%20people's%20houses%20has%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20so%20far%3F%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20information.%20Ganesh%20festival%20is%20celebrated%20in%20many%20places%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20went%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20house%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20together%20performed%20the%20Aarti.%20Our%20knowledge%20of%20God%20is%20such%20that%20if%20the%20custodians%20of%20the%20Constitution%20meet%20political%20leaders%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20then%20people%20have%20doubts%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20there%20is%20a%20tradition%20that%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20party%20and%20the%20judge%20has%20or%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20any%20relation%20with%20it%2C%20then%20he%20dissociates%20himself%20from%20that%20case.%20So%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20Chandrachud%20sahab%20should%20dissociate%20himself%20from%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Jha%2C%20RJD%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20had%20said%20the%20independence%20of%20institutions%20must%20be%20seen.%20%26quot%3BGanpati%20puja%20is%20a%20personal%20issue%2C%20but%20you%20are%20taking%20a%20camera.%20The%20message%20it%20sends%20is%20uncomfortable.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20are%20tall%20personalities.%20So%20what%20can%20we%20say%20if%20they%20agreed%20to%20put%20out%20these%20photographs%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20had%20responded%20sharply%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism.%20Union%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20said%20the%20people%20who%20applaud%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Ministers%20at%20Iftar%20parties%20%26quot%3Bfind%20their%20guts%20twisting%20and%20turning%26quot%3B%20on%20seeing%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20the%20Ganesh%20Puja%20at%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20people%20who%20applaud%20and%20encourage%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Ministers%20at%20Iftars%20find%20their%20guts%20twisting%20and%20turning%20when%20they%20see%20PM%20Modi%20perform%20Ganpati%20Poojan%20at%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud's%20residence.%20The%20executive%20and%20judiciary%20praying%20before%20Gods%20revered%20by%20crores%20of%20devotees%20across%20India%20reflects%20the%20real%20strength%20of%20Indian%20secularism.%20Deal%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20criticism%2C%20commenting%20that%20a%202009%20Iftar%20party%20hosted%20by%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20attended%20by%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20KG%20Balakrishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20is%20set%20to%20retire%20on%20November%2010.%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20will%20succeed%20him%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730102280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjtu40si8_pm-cji_625x300_12_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-pm-narendra-modi-no-bearing-on-judicial-work-chief-justice-on-pms-ganesh-puja-visit-row-6890881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20massive%20political%20row%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20his%20home%20for%20Ganesh%20Puja%2C%20saying%20no%20judicial%20matters%20are%20discussed%20in%20such%20meetings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-pm-narendra-modi-no-bearing-on-judicial-work-chief-justice-on-pms-ganesh-puja-visit-row-6890881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kartik%3A%20It%20feels%20Vidya%20and%20I%20went%20to%20college%20together%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730101762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114683893%2Cimgsize-27084.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkartik-aaryan-it-feels-vidya-balan-and-i-went-to-college-together-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F114683893.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114683893.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210