20for%20new%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Babynama%20has%20since%20added%20new%20programmes%20to%20meet%20the%20evolving%20needs%20of%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoms%20began%20asking%20questions%20about%20breastfeeding%2C%20starting%20solids%2C%20nutritious%20meals%2C%20and%20sleep.%20To%20solve%20these%20queries%2C%20we%20onboarded%20lactation%20experts%2C%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20sleep%20specialists%2C%20and%20created%20programmes%20around%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Sumitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabynama%E2%80%99s%20plans%20start%20at%20Rs%20499.%20The%20%3Cem%3EEssential%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20plan%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%2C999%2C%20provides%20access%20to%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20with%20paediatricians%2C%2024%2F7%20video%20consultations%2C%20and%20monthly%20milestone%20check-ups.%20Their%20%3Cem%3EHolistic%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20plan%2C%20which%20includes%20access%20to%20a%20dedicated%20paediatrician%20in%20a%20private%20group%20along%20with%20breastfeeding%20and%20nutrition%20support%2C%20is%20available%20for%20Rs%203%2C999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20offer%20specialised%20programmes%20such%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ESolids%20Introduction%20Course%2C%20Breastfeeding%20Training%20Program%2C%20Baby%20Nutrition%20Program%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20Sleep%20Training%20Program%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20%3Cem%3EHolistic%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20remains%20their%20bestseller%2C%20with%207%2C200%20paid%20customers%2C%20while%20over%20two%20lakh%20people%20have%20attended%20their%20free%20webinars.%20Their%20Instagram%20page%20has%20garnered%20over%20four%20and%20a%20half%20lakh%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3z-C9ZJqbo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3z-C9ZJqbo%2F%3Futm_source%