uploads%2F2024%2F10%2F2-29-min-1729856850.jpg%3Fresize%3D1997%252C2048%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201997w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2F2-29-min-1729856850.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C154%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sumitra%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Ashish%20Meena%2C%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20join%20Babynama%20as%20co-founder%20to%20support%20the%20mission.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Sumitra%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20resources%20to%20parents%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20newborn%20or%20a%20five-year-old%2C%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%20%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20make%20quality%20healthcare%20accessible%2C%20no%20matter%20which%20corner%20of%20the%20country%20you%20are%20in.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20lose%20their%20child%20like%20my%20parents%20did%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabynama%20also%20plans%20to%20make%20its%20services%20more%20affordable%2C%20aiming%20to%20reach%20all%20sections%20of%20society.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20AI%20(Artificial%20Intelligence)%2C%20they%20are%20building%20a%20chatbot%20on%20their%20app%2C%20which%20will%20have%20answers%20to%20common%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20can%20simply%20download%20the%20app%2C%20ask%20a%20question%2C%20and%20get%20an%20answer.%20In%20case%20they%20need%20further%20assistance%2C%20they%20can%20book%20a%20consultation.%20We%20are%20planning%20to%20launch%20plans%20starting%20from%20Rs%2099%20per%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Sumitra%2C%20the%20most%20satisfying%20part%20has%20been%20helping%20parents.%20She%20recounts%20her%20first%20call%2C%20where%20she%20diagnosed%20a%20child%20with%20autism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20c