tiative%20%E2%80%94%20an%20annual%20constituency-based%20competition%20for%20students%20every%20December%2C%20including%20essays%2C%20quizzes%2C%20maths%2C%20and%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrivate%20school%20students%20often%20have%20infrastructural%20advantages.%20My%20father%20wanted%20government%20school%20students%20to%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20on%20par%20with%20others.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20started%20the%20competition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chinglensana%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%2C%20Chinglensana%20is%20pursuing%20a%20career%20aimed%20at%20educating%20and%20training%20children.%20His%20current%20position%20at%20%E2%80%98Lend%20A%20Hand%2C%20India%E2%80%99%20allows%20him%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20vocational%20training%20module%20for%20children%20in%20Nagaland.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20gather%20the%20necessary%20experience%20so%20that%20I%20can%20help%20my%20father%20in%20a%20better%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAddressing%20student%20dropout%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20school%20was%20upgraded%20to%20an%20upper%20primary%20school%3B%20that%20same%20year%2C%20Indrakumar%20received%20the%20National%20Teachers%20Award%20for%20his%20contributions%20to%20primary%20education.%20However%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20students%20dropping%20out%20at%20such%20young%20ages%20continued%20to%20trouble%20him%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20seek%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20children%20studying%20in%20my%20school.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20dropping%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%